                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">3.2 Client Responsibilities</h5>
                    <p>You agree to:</p>
                    <ul class="mb-3">
                        <li>Provide all necessary content, materials, and information in a timely manner</li>
                        <li>Respond to requests for feedback within the agreed timeframe (typically 3-5 business days)</li>
