                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">4.1 Payment Structure</h5>
                    <ul class="mb-3">
                        <li><strong>Deposit:</strong> Typically 50% required to begin work</li>
                        <li><strong>Final Payment:</strong> Remaining balance due upon project completion</li>
                        <li><strong>Large Projects:</strong> May be broken into milestone-based payments</li>
                        <li><strong>Monthly Services:</strong> Billed at the beginning of each month</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">4.2 Payment Methods</h5>
                    <p>We accept:</p>
                    <ul class="mb-3">
                        <li>Bank transfer/ACH</li>
                        <li>Credit/debit cards (processing fees may apply)</li>
                        <li>PayPal or similar payment platforms</li>
                        <li>Check (for established clients)</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">4.3 Late Payments</h5>
                    <ul class="mb-3">
                        <li>Invoices are due within 7 days of issue unless otherwise specified</li>
                        <li>Late payments may incur a 5% fee after 14 days</li>
                        <li>Work may be paused for accounts more than 14 days overdue</li>
                        <li>Final deliverables will not be released until full payment is received</li>
                    </ul>

